 151:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** /**
 152:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Sets Timestamp.
 153:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note   This API must be called before enabling the Timestamp feature.
 154:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  hrtc pointer to a RTC_HandleTypeDef structure that contains
 155:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                the configuration information for RTC.
 156:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampEdge Specifies the pin edge on which the Timestamp is
 157:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         activated.
 158:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 159:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_RISING: the Timestamp event occurs on
 160:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                        the rising edge of the related pin.
 161:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_FALLING: the Timestamp event occurs on
 162:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                        the falling edge of the related pin.
 163:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampPin Specifies the RTC Timestamp Pin.
 164:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 165:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPPIN_DEFAULT: PC13 is selected as RTC Timestamp Pin.
 166:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note RTC_TIMESTAMPPIN_DEFAULT corresponds to pin:
 167:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *       - PC13 in the case of STM32L05x/6x/7x/8x devices
 168:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *       - PA2 in the case of STM32L01x/2x/3x/4x devices
 169:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note Although unused, parameter RTC_TimeStampPin has been kept for portability
