1624:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** /**
1625:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Configures the Synchronization Shift Control Settings.
1626:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note   When REFCKON is set, firmware must not write to Shift control register.
1627:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  hrtc pointer to a RTC_HandleTypeDef structure that contains
1628:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                the configuration information for RTC.
1629:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  ShiftAdd1S Select to add or not 1 second to the time calendar.
1630:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
1631:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SHIFTADD1S_SET: Add one second to the clock calendar.
